gui.meansOfTransportInfo.intro: You can choose the Means of transport from several options. Changing the value can have an impact on other sections of the form.
gui.meansOfTransportInfo.panels.title: Disabling/Enablig panels
gui.meansOfTransportInfo.panels.descript: The Document, cargo handling and companies panels are desabled by default. You can enable them if one of the Means of transport blocks has the value "commercial vessel", "road", "railway/train" or "air cargo".
gui.meansOfTransportInfo.panels.warning: If you have entered data in those panels and later decide to remove all those types of means of transport, the panels will be disabled and you will lose all the data.
gui.meansOfTransportInfo.cargo.title: Air Cargo Panel
gui.meansOfTransportInfo.cargo.descripti: The following rules apply depending on the selected value of Means of transport:
gui.meansOfTransportInfo.cargo.uldRule: You can add ULDs only if one of the blocks has Air Cargo as the selected value.
gui.meansOfTransportInfo.cargo.container: Containers only if one of the blocks has Commercial Vessel, Road or Railway as the selected value
gui.meansOfTransportInfo.cargo.warning: When one of the section is disabled, all data entered will be removed.
gui.meansOfTransportInfo.routings.title: Connexion with routings
gui.meansOfTransportInfo.routings.descri: Each routing is linked to a Means of transport, therefore changing the value will delete all the routings related to it.
gui.meansOfTransportInfo.routings.warnin: When a routing section is removed, all data of that section will be lost.
